OL,6,FThe most recent rounds of cuts to BBC
OL,7,Fservices have taken place with little
OL,8,For no consultation. What information
OL,9,Fhas been shared has been mostly
OL,10,Fhigh-level, with a more detailed
OL,11,Fbreakdown missing.
OL,13,FA number of commercial broadcasters are
OL,14,Funderstood to be unhappy with the way
OL,15,Fthe BBC is requesting reductions or
OL,16,Fremovals of quotas.
