OL,6,FChanges have been implemented with
OL,7,Flittle or no notice. The BBC declined
OL,8,Fto publish updated schedules showing
OL,9,Fwhat would replace The Papers on the
OL,10,FNews Channel until the day after the
OL,11,Flast edition aired.
OL,13,FThe BBC World Service was originally
OL,14,Ffunded through the Foreign and
OL,15,FCommonwealth Office. This changed
OL,16,Fduring the first licence fee freeze
OL,17,Fthat ran from 2011 to 2016, when the
OL,18,FBBC was asked to shoulder the cost of
OL,19,FS4C, the World Service and the rollout
OL,20,Fof local TV in addition to funding its
OL,21,Fown services.
